<p>``` ruby</p>

<h1>!/usr/bin/env ruby</h1>

<p>app_path = File.expand_path(&ldquo;../&rdquo;, File.dirname(<strong>FILE</strong>))</p>

<p>boot_path =  File.join(app_path,&ldquo;boot&rdquo;)</p>

<p>command = &ldquo;irb -r irb/completion -r #{boot_path}&rdquo;
exec command
```</p>
